title: Annyit ésszel, mint erővel
overview: As much wit as strength! the game in which both physical and mental performance are important. In each broadcast, a boy and a girl compete, in the first half of the game they perform tasks as a team, but later they duel each other so that in the final game only the winner plays for the cash prize, which can be HUF 10 million. In the gigantic, colorful scenery, you have to perform fun physics competitions at the same time, and at the same time there is a quiz game. If the couples can play together, if they are smart and skilled enough, one of them can easily become a millionaire!
